data.description: At 7942 S Paulina, find a multi-unit property that embodies both the charm of generational family ownership and the allure of modern updates. It's a prime pick for investors or those eyeing a home with income-generating prospects. The building features recently updated essentials, including a range of kitchen appliances-oven, refrigerator, and freezer-all new within the last two months. The interiors are refreshed with renovated kitchens and bathrooms, polished hardwood floors, and a fresh coat of paint throughout. Accommodations are spacious, with each unit offering ample living and dining space, plus eat-in kitchens. The addition of a new 3-car garage and back porch deck rounds out the property's conveniences. The property's location offers convenient access to essential amenities, providing a practical living environment. Plus, with the option for a 5% down payment, it's an accessible choice for those looking to invest. Don't miss out on the opportunity at 7942 S Paulina, where the promise of income potential and modern living awaits.
